{"text_id":250356,"tokens":["In"," this"," work",","," we"," investigate"," the"," cosmology"," of"," modified"," Gauss","-","Bon","net"," gravity",","," which"," is"," an"," extension"," of"," General"," Relativity","."," The"," key"," idea"," behind"," this"," theory"," is"," that"," the"," Gauss","-","Bon","net"," term",","," which"," is"," a"," curvature"," invariant",","," is"," added"," to"," the"," Einstein","-","Hil","bert"," action",","," giving"," rise"," to"," an"," additional"," contribution"," to"," the"," gravitational"," field"," equations","."," We"," study"," the"," cosmological"," implications"," of"," this"," modification",","," focusing"," on"," the"," early"," universe"," and"," the"," inflationary"," era",".","Our"," methodology"," involves"," the"," numerical"," integration"," of"," the"," cosmological"," equations"," for"," a"," variety"," of"," initial"," conditions",","," exploring"," the"," parameter"," space"," of"," the"," theory","."," We"," use"," the"," Planck"," data"," on"," the"," cosmic"," microwave"," background"," radiation"," to"," constrain"," the"," parameters"," of"," the"," model",","," and"," compare"," the"," theoretical"," predictions"," with"," observations","."," We"," find"," that"," the"," modified"," Gauss","-","Bon","net"," gravity"," is"," capable"," of"," providing"," a"," viable"," alternative"," to"," the"," standard"," inflationary"," paradigm",","," with"," several"," interesting"," features"," such"," as"," the"," possibility"," of"," a"," graceful"," exit"," from"," inflation"," and"," a"," reduction"," in"," the"," tensor","-","to","-","scalar"," ratio",".","The"," main"," motivation"," for"," this"," research"," is"," to"," explore"," the"," consequences"," of"," modifying"," gravity"," at"," the"," cosmological"," scale",","," in"," the"," light"," of"," the"," current"," observational"," data","."," Our"," results"," indicate"," that"," the"," modified"," Gauss","-","Bon","net"," gravity"," can"," provide"," a"," compelling"," cosmological"," model",","," worth"," further"," investigation"," in"," the"," search"," for"," a"," complete"," theory"," of"," gravity","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"gpt-3.5-turbo","label":1}